entries.title_d: Protect a medical freighter from Black Sun aggression.
entries.title: Naboo System: Escort emergency medical transport to safety
entries.thanks_5: Awesome piloting my friend, hopefully that was the last of them.
entries.thanks_4: Yes! That's how you take care of that pirate scum!
entries.thanks_3: I see the RSF reputation is not just a rumor after all!
entries.thanks_2: Nice going pilot! Keep it up, I got a feeling it's not over yet.
entries.taunt_5: Everyone is the property of the Black Sun, they just don't know it yet!
entries.taunt_4: Pack yourself out of here RSF drone, we're taking this ship.
entries.taunt_3: Your whole organisation is a joke RSF pilot, everyone knows that the Black Sun rules here.
entries.taunt_2: Don't even think about it RSF fool, no one gets in the way of the Black Sun!
entries.taunt_1: The Black Sun claim the content of this transport. Step back or face the consequences.
entries.split_quest_alert_fail: \#pcontrast3 Capt Dinge: < \#pcontrast1 You appear to have hit a little snag out there Captain.  Get patched up and run that patrol again. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 Capt Dinge: < \#pcontrast1 You appear to have hit a little snag out there Captain.  Get patched up and run that patrol again. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.shields_depleted: Our shields are depleted pilot, we can't take many more hits like that!
entries.reason_5: We're transporting emergency medical supplies for victims of the terrrorist attack on Theed. Please make sure we get through safely!

entries.quest_rendezvous_d: Travel to this point to meet the medical freighter.
entries.quest_escort_d: A heavy freighter transporting medical supplies.
entries.panic_4: Thugs on attack vector! We're not built for fighting, it's all up to you pilot!
entries.panic_3: Pirates! I hope your up to this pilot!
entries.panic_2: Fighter vessels incoming, they don't look friendly!
entries.panic_1: Pirate scum incoming, I hope you can handle this!
entries.hull_half: We have multiple hull breeches! I'm preparing a emergency hyperspace jump. If you can't protect us we're going to have to bail!
entries.goodbye_5: Phew, we made it! Thank you pilot, we couldn't have done it without you!
entries.goodbye_4: Phew, we made it! Thank you pilot, we couldn't have done it without you!
entries.goodbye_3: Excellent work Captain, we are making the jump now.
entries.goodbye_2: These medicines will be most welcome.
entries.goodbye_1: Phew, we made it! Thank you pilot, we couldn't have done it without you!
entries.found_loc: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Escort meeting coordinates uploaded. Proceed as soon as possible. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.failed_protect: I can't take on these pirates on my own! I'm doing a emergency jump to hyperspace!
entries.failed_destroy: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 That poor transport never had a chance. Report back to your superior for a full report immediately. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.complete: The Transport is safe. Great job up there, report back to base for further instructions.
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 No more fighter vessels within sensor range. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed.  \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_loc: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Arrived at rendezvous. Transport should be here momentarily. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.abort: You have failed because you aborted the mission.
